                <p>verse poems-Bancroft-1969-Gaki stopped mailing a this letter at the last moment - to reconsider a
                day or two- 
                He never did want it sent
                finally -</p> 
                <p>I have inquired at Bancroft about Converse-He is established in New York &amp; doing well by 1972</p>
                <closer>
